makeNew

public void makeNew()

readSudoku

public void readSudoku()
This method reads the sudoku from a file. This method reads just 81 characters on a single line. So that behind the sudoku, it is possible to put some comments about the sudoku being read.

updateTo2d

public int[][] updateTo2d()
Creates a 2d board from the 3d board. A 2d board is generated from the 3d board, so it can be used for backtracking. As backtracking with a 3d board would be inefficient and very difficult.

Returns:
The 2d sudoku.

public boolean checkSolved()
